{"tid":341965,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"化學撚想求出路，請指教","createTime":"2017-07-31T08:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T09:38:48.000Z","uid":131208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed22701e29cb4e0e5239623fa23a5b6d329d71c7","tid":341965,"uid":131208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:32:03.000Z","msg":"小弟chem degree 2nd low grad，<br />\n之後仲要懵撚左讀左個MSc food safety，<br />\n結果冇人承認搞到要踎補習社維持生計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟就趁而家d小朋友放暑假得閒，<br />\n就諗左幾條後路，<br />\n小弟明白其實條條路都係做狗（Dog）<br />\n但都希望搵條路冇咁狗，<br />\n還望各位巴絲指教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. PGDE做教畜<br />\n呢個似乎最正路同最多人揀，但可能讀完後未必有教席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 醫療化驗MLT<br />\n小弟搵過下資料好似冇postgrad course讀完後即刻有牌（有錯請指正）<br />\n但醫務化驗委員會個網話part II註冊資格有呢個條款：<br />\n<br />\n委 員 會 頒 發 的 證 明 書 ， 證 明 其 通 過 與 醫 務 化 驗 師 專 業 有 關 的 考 試 ， 而 該 考 試 是 為 施 行 本 條 例 第 1 2 ( 1 ) ( a ) 條 而 根 據 本 條 例 第 1 5 A 條 主 持 的<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.smp-council.org.hk/mlt/tc/content.php?page=reg_quareg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.smp-council.org.hk%2Fmlt%2Ftc%2Fcontent.php%3Fpage%3Dreg_quareg&d=yX%2F66xiNI6rdAY%2FZDkS4LxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=2edcc4fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.smp-council.org.hk/mlt/tc/content.php?page=reg_quareg</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟想問下呢個試可以點報？係咪交左註冊申請表就得？<br />\n或者有冇做緊呢行既巴絲講下有冇識人透過呢個試入行？<br />\n前景又係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 香港測檢認證協會註冊化驗師<br />\n呢個要做幾年lab狗再考佢個試先有，感覺好似仲伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hktic.org/template?series=4&amp;article=54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hktic.org%2Ftemplate%3Fseries%3D4%26article%3D54&d=yX%2F66xiNI6rdAY%2FZDkS4LxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=b94f40e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hktic.org/template?series=4&amp;article=54</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲可以比下意見，感激萬分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b903eed6d7e1e3497036af9b1d6d016dcab1e6","tid":341965,"uid":131208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc59528568ee6d3c02aca38034904588b31e7aa3","tid":341965,"uid":131208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f368eb6ebc957f4dbaab06f35201e3e7cb4db0c7","tid":341965,"uid":15818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"做lab做成世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做到30歲應該有20k既 （連加班）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046c2e8384c107c07eeb89b66787ca7f79debe5e","tid":341965,"uid":131208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做lab做成世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做到30歲應該有20k既 （連加班）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁如果齋講人工既我而家做緊間補習社都可以搵10-35k既<br />\n但好似冇咩前景咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以先想討論下"},{"pid":"b9a3c46bfd916934c950005a652d793323db7925","tid":341965,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做lab做成世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做到30歲應該有20k既 （連加班）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 